            "id": 6397446,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 邑昇(5291)大漲7.06%，報78.9元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>邑昇(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5291:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5291\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5291-TW</a>)26日13:02股價上漲5.2元，報78.9元，漲幅7.06%，成交13,533張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>邑昇(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5291:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5291\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5291-TW</a>)所屬產業為電子零組件業，主要業務為印刷電路板。光電產品。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲20.94%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌5.06%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+1,007 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+994 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+13 張</li> <li>融資增減：+17 張</li> <li>融券增減：+64 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
